      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #363131;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    ">
    <span style="font-weight: 500">Hello <%= name %>,</span>
    <br /><br />
    Forgot your password? To reset your password please user to OTP code to
    reset your password <br />
